x_example.Rd

Path to directory containing example data.

x_example(path = ".")

Arguments

path

Path to a file (with extension) from inst/extdata/

Value

A string giving a path to an example.

Examples

dir(x_example())
#> [1] "taxa.csv"      "vft_4quad.csv"
read.csv(x_example("taxa.csv"))[1:5, 1:5]
#>   ViewID SpeciesID SubspeciesID                  Family Mnemonic
#> 1      1        56           NA                Fabaceae   AESAME
#> 2      2        57           NA           Euphorbiaceae   ALCFLO
#> 3      3        58           NA           Euphorbiaceae   ALCLAT
#> 4      4        59           NA Fabaceae-papilionoideae   ANDINE
#> 5      5        60           NA               Rubiaceae   ANTOBT
